Strict mode - Imposes a lot of restrictions in our JS code.

just put in "use strict";
Just it is used to ensure no bugs come in due to the leniency that JS gives us while writing code
While using React, Strict mode is always on

Normal Functions vs Arrow Functions

In Normal Functions, "this" keyword is undefined.

In Arrow Functions, "this" keyword is not undefined.